<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-07-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-07-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="214" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d214">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.911/32.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                Minister <persName type="to">Gonzales</persName>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 98.]</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-07-28">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 28, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The Department has received your No. 123
                            of the 11th instant inclosing a copy of a letter addressed by you to
                            President Menocal, in which you stated that the time already served by
                            Enrique Maza might well be considered by the Cuban Government as
                            sufficient satisfaction of his sentence, and that this Government had no
                            desire for his longer confinement.</p>
                        <p>The Department approves your action.</p>
                        <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                        <closer>For the Secretary of State: <lb/>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">John E. Osborne</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>